Description: Directly selecting differentially expressed genes for single-cell clustering analyses via EM-test. "Festem" also provides EM-test to test whether the number of component in mixtures of normal, Poisson or negative binomial distributions are larger than one. See Chen, Wang, et al (2024) <https://doi.org/10.1016/j.crmeth.2024.100810> and Wang, Chen and Xi (2023) <https://doi.org/10.48550/arXiv.2306.12671> for more details.
